1
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,320
Yan Qingshu.

2
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,880
I wondered what kind of noble person it was.

3
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,160
Turns out,

4
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:25,289
you're just a lowly child born of a concubine.

5
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,920
Qingshu.

6
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:39,720
You bitch.

7
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,080
You're actually not dead.

8
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,080
Acting so recklessly on my turf.

9
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,660
Are you in a rush to get reincarnated?

10
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,370
Marquis of Zhenbei's Mansion.

11
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,320
Qingshu,

12
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:10,880
when did you get involved with the Marquis of Zhenbei's Mansion?

13
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,760
This slap

14
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:16,079
is to thank you for the annulment letter.

15
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:16,760
Qingshu,

16
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,240
listen to me.

17
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,840
Annuling the engagement

18
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,170
was never my intention.

19
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,440
That day,

20
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,800
I was also forced into it.

21
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,240
Actually, I...

22
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:32,000
I will take back all the pain I suffered before,

23
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,760
twice over.

24
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:38,360
You want to seduce Brother Yuheng.

25
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,290
To rekindle your romance with him?

26
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,680
How dare you hit me!

27
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,360
You!

28
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,890
It seems you don't want this hand anymore.

29
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,570
Please show mercy, sir.

30
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,520
We offended you today.

31
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:07,040
Please be generous and let us go.

32
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,520
Recently, I heard that

33
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:18,170
the Xie family and the Right Worthy Prince of Northern Di

34
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:21,520
have been exchanging letters and colluding secretly.

35
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,520
He seems to have an ulterior motive.

36
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,170
I don't know if this news

37
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:28,200
is true or false.

38
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,640
Next time, arrange that little matchmaker

39
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,680
for my lord.

40
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,200
Right.

41
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,720
That matchmaker's skills

42
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,400
are indeed unforgettable.

43
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,079
Right, right, right.

44
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,480
What? Have you tried her?

45
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,160
I only heard about it.

46
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,579
My lord.

47
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,840
There's no time like the present.

48
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,320
How about it?

49
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,560
You know me well, boy.

50
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,600
Mr. Wang hoarded

51
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:01,280
hundreds of thousands of silver taels in his Qingzhou villa.

52
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,610
Have you heard about it?

53
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,280
I've heard a thing or two.

54
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,640
More than that.

55
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,400
My lord,

56
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,800
outside the mansion,

57
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,930
they even keep seventeen concubines.

58
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,050
Corrupt officials.

59
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,800
It seems Lady Qin of Yaowang Valley

60
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,200
has passed all her real skills to you, Miss.

61
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,480
Aunt Qin taught me

62
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:27,480
to identify poisons, use acupuncture, and prescribe medicine.

63
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,160
Now,

64
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,400
healing the sick

65
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,920
and poisoning to kill

66
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,760
are all at my fingertips.

67
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,080
You are kind-hearted, Miss.

68
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,480
As for poisoning to kill,

69
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,740
I don't believe you could learn that.

70
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,040
My Lady.

71
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:45,840
I heard some gossip in the tea room today.

72
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,659
A few guests mentioned

73
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,480
that Master was falsely accused of treason back then.

74
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,480
The late emperor was furious and ordered his execution.

75
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,080
However, before the decree arrived,

76
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,480
Master had disappeared.

77
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,840
But Master was definitely not a traitor.

78
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:00,580
There must be a hidden truth behind this.

79
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,240
That scene in the hall today

80
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,090
was truly spectacular.

81
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,010
This is just the beginning.

82
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,360
I'm just curious.

83
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,240
Those last words you said to Xie Yuheng,

84
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,920
were they to scare him

85
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,540
or for revenge?

86
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,120
None of your business.

87
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,600
If you have nothing else,

88
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,620
I'll go boil the medicine.

89
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,200
Miss Yan,

90
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,210
you really are unromantic.

91
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:40,040
It seems it's just my wishful thinking.

92
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,440
In three days,

93
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:58,480
Xie Yuheng will personally escort a batch of military provisions

94
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,800
to the Northern Camp.

95
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,580
You want to hijack the provisions

96
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,410
and frame him for delaying military operations?

97
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:12,010
For a mere dereliction of duty,

98
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,700
why go to all this trouble?

99
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,440
I want to send him to his grave.

100
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,040
He will definitely take the waterway.

101
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,970
I will have set up an ambush by then,

102
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,300
guaranteeing nothing will go wrong.

103
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,680
Since I've done you such a big favor,

104
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:37,880
tonight,

105
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,300
would you be willing to go somewhere with me?

106
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,400
I actually forgot

107
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,160
that today is the Lantern Festival.

108
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:03,880
It's fine.

109
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,240
You can forget the small things

110
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,570
as long as you remember the great revenge.

111
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,280
Mother always said

112
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,580
that folding a lantern

113
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:30,560
can wash away all bad luck down the river.

114
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,200
From now on,

115
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,760
your bad luck

116
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,240
is half mine.

117
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,400
Mother, look!

118
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,730
It's a carp lantern.

119
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,920
So beautiful.

120
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,540
The show is about to start.

121
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,720
Sanniang.

122
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,880
Miss.

123
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,040
Didn't you go to see the lanterns with Mr. Ren?

124
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:06,600
Why are you back so early?

125
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:10,250
Maybe this year's lantern festival has nothing new.

126
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:11,680
By the way.

127
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:14,480
Today, the governor and his two assistant magistrates

128
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,120
talked about Cangzhou's military pay.

129
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,680
That old guy Wang Lang,

130
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,420
he actually hid 300,000 taels of silver.

131
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,000
Miss.

132
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,850
I am sitting here right now.

133
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,520
Bitch.

134
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,760
Go and atone for your sins

135
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,340
with your jinx master.

136
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,559
You are not Qingshu.

137
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:53,200
Yan Mingli.

138
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:55,800
At 5:45 PM,

139
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:59,760
the Xie family will be under the largest carp lantern on East Street

140
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:02,090
to hand over the secret letter from Beidi.

141
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,680
Take care, sir.

142
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,640
Buy a drum.

143
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,160
I'm not buying.

144
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:22,880
Just buy one.

145
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:25,010
Why are you pushing it against my head?

146
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:25,800
I said I'm not buying.

147
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:26,460
Take a look.

148
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,200
I said I don't want it.

149
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,800
I said no.

150
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,560
No.

151
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:32,680
Move.

152
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,770
Why go to all the trouble to swap it?

153
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,280
Wouldn't it be simpler to just destroy it?

154
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,240
This is hard evidence of Xie Yuheng colluding

155
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,320
with the Right Worthy Prince of Northern Di.

156
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,320
If I destroy it,

157
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,280
they can just write another one.

158
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,260
We might as well

159
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,720
let it serve its greatest purpose.

160
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,880
Tampering with the letter

161
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,900
and altering its contents...

162
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,280
The goal is to

163
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,640
turn Northern Di and the Xie family against each other.

164
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:16,280
Smart.

165
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,640
In three days,

166
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:22,340
Xie Yuheng will die on his way escorting the military rations.

167
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,560
Meanwhile,

168
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,760
the envoy sent by Northern Di to the capital

169
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,330
will also die accidentally

170
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:31,170
in the Xie family's secondary residence.

171
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:33,440
Silencing them

172
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,200
and framing others.

173
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,560
At the very least,

174
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,160
Xie Wanshu will retire and return home.

175
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,080
At worst,

176
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,400
he will pay with his life.

177
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:46,860
Your Highness,

178
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,800
the deal with Northern Di

179
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,640
may need to be postponed.

180
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,280
Our recent movements,

181
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,440
I'm afraid,

182
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:56,240
have been noticed by others.

183
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,800
Xiao Jingyan.

184
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:03,000
Although there is no hard evidence.

185
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,860
But looking at the whole capital,

186
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,560
who else would have the guts

187
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,690
to provoke you, Your Highness?

188
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:11,320
He was able to intercept our secret letter.

189
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,120
I'm afraid

190
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,920
what he has in his hands

191
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,400
is far more than that.

192
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:20,480
Xie Yuheng,

193
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:21,960
you are wrong.

194
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,120
It's not our secret letter.

195
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:27,000
It's yours and Beidi's.

196
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,280
Yes,

197
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,640
I misspoke.

198
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,490
The father is already dead.

199
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,200
What waves

200
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:39,160
can the son make?

201
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,440
I have never taken him seriously.

202
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,640
You are wise, Your Highness.

203
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,560
Cuimei

204
